item.title: [HBASE-4670] Fix javadoc warnings
item.description: We have hundreds of javadoc warnings emitted on every build.

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are closed can be reopened.

comments.comment: Committed to 0.92 branch and trunk. Neither have warnings now.
